  ('medical-tech-moex-12278', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-102-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關水泡狀胎塊（hydatidiform mole）之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["完全型水泡狀胎塊（complete hydatidiform mole）的滋養層細胞增生經常是局部且輕微的", "部分型水泡狀胎塊（patial hydatidiform mole），幾乎所有的絨毛（villi）都呈現顯著的水腫", "大約2%的完全型水泡狀胎塊會有發展成絨毛膜癌（choriocarcinoma）的可能性", "部分型水泡狀胎塊的主要核型（karyotype）是46,XX"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:45+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "311b1a6bc3f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a1873b17ffd2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102100", "c": "311", "s": "11", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第二次專技牙醫師分試藥師醫事檢驗師醫放師助產師物理治療師職能治療師呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 61, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
